Santa's lap anymore.''
</P>
<P>
   Sites offering wish lists:
</P>
<P>
   www.amazon.com
</P>
<P>
   www.etoys.com
</P>
<P>
   www.fastfrog.com
</P>
<P>
   www.alloy.com
</P>
<P>
   www.rei.com
</P>
<P>
   www.della.com
</P>
<P>
   www.secretwish.com
</P>
<P>
   Detail from www.amazon.com
</P>
<P>
   Frances Katz writes for the Atlanta Journal-Constitution.
