afternoons by 5 p.m. Keying to the Monday wrestling events, It's
good for publication any day through Sunday. Here are the elements
on the page, which are also moving on the entertainment wire:
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-GIFTS _ What do you get the wrestling fan who has
everything? (Allen, Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-GRAPEVINE _News, notes and gossip from the world of
professional wrestling.
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-WWF _ Fallout from WWF's toning down the violence and
sex appeal of its show. (Allen, Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
