<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-08 12:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2810 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u t BC-TRAVEL-COLLINS-BOS &LR;      12-08 1241
