   GRANDMOTHER-GUN (Albany, N.Y.) _ Gun-totin' granny Hildegard von
Waldenburg never thought she'd live to see 2000, never mind be
facing a possible year in jail for pulling a shotgun on a Nassau
road crew that was cutting her trees in February. By MICHELE MORGAN
BOLTON.
