<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-08 13:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2894 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k BC-JACKSON-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      12-08 0889
