   www.gourmetmarket.com: A gourmand's delight: wines, chocolates,
cheeses, gift baskets.
</P>
<P>
   www.harryanddavid.com: Catalog staple features fruits.
</P>
<P>
   www.enricobiscotti.com: Traditional Italian pastries, from
macaroons to tortas.
</P>
<P>
   www.latingrocer.com: This bilingual site features Caribbean,
Mexican and Spanish foods.
</P>
<P>
   www.balducci.com: Famous New York Italian deli goes online.
</P>
<P>
   www.tavolo.com: Specialty foods, gourmet kitchenware.
</P>
<P>
   www.wine.com: Informative site that sells wine.
</P>
<P>
   www.peets.com: Fine deep-roasted coffees and tea.
</P>
<P>
   www.collinstreetbakery. com: Corsicana bakery famous for
fruitcake ships all over the world.
</P>
