   Books, music and videos
</P>
<P>
   www.ccvideo.com: Choose from 61,000 VHS and DVD titles. New
releases, British videos and hard to find films.
</P>
<P>
   www.reel.com: Promises the lowest online prices for movies and
backs it up with a guarantee.
</P>
<P>
   www.bopshop.com: Sells collectible vinyl, reel-to-reels and CDs
showcasing blues and jazz.
</P>
