<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-08 13:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2994 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a BC-CPT-TECH-TOOLS07-COX &LR;      12-08 0633
