   CIR-PHONE-DESIGNER (Undated) _ Who designed that cool phone
Keanu Reeves used in The Matrix, and that was given as a party
favor to winners at the Emmy awards? Profile of Frank Nuovo, Nokia
designer who has become the prime tastemaker in what is
increasingly becoming a fashion accessory as well as a tool, the
cell phone. By Katie Hafner.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   With sidebar $800-PHONE-SALES, on the marketing of hot new $799
phone to see how many people actually buy that kind of thing. By
Katie Hafner.
