<P>
   CLINTON-CONFERENCE (Washington) _ In a wide-ranging news
conference, President Clinton rejects severing aid to Russia as a
response to its siege of the restive region of Chechnya. And the
president looks back on a year that included the impeachment trial
against him and some major foreign policy failures. By NANCY
MATHIS.
