picture has suffered during its conversion from the crowded CD-ROM
market to the burgeoning game console niche. Vincent Bitetti said
he believes the company will survive and thrive, all with a new
auditor. By Jason Z. Cohen. (Will move in the ``f'' financial news
wire.)
</P>
