responded, ``Aaah!'' Which is better than laughing about it, as my
kid would have surely done.
</P>
<P>
   (Eric Celeste's Hey, Dad column appears every other Tuesday.
Visit the Star-Telegram's online services on the World Wide Web:
www.star-telegram.com) &QL; 
</P>
</TEXT>
